HAJDE!

945
01:34:27,495 --> 01:34:29,496
PROBILI SMO ZID KAPETANE,

946
01:34:29,498 --> 01:34:31,464
ALI SMO IZGUBILI MNOGO LJUDI.

947
01:34:31,466 --> 01:34:35,101
MORAMO POBIJEDITI.
BORIÆEMO SE DO SAMOG KRAJA.

948
01:34:36,972 --> 01:34:38,772
DOLAZE DRUGI KAPETANI!

949
01:34:55,423 --> 01:34:57,323
GOSPODARU,VAŠ BRAT JE MRTAV.

950
01:34:57,325 --> 01:35:00,427
PREDAJEMO SE TEBI
I TVOM PLEMENITOM CILJU.

951
01:35:00,429 --> 01:35:03,430
